name: FakeValuesService_primitiveToWrapperTest
description: Unit tests for the primitiveToWrapper method in the FakeValuesService class.

test_cases.name: testPrimitiveToWrapper
test_cases.description: Tests the conversion of a primitive class to its wrapper class and verifies that a non-primitive class remains unchanged.

test_cases.name: testPrimitiveToWrapperWithNull
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of the primitiveToWrapper method when a null class is provided, expecting a null result.
